But the main thing is that now we know. Now we are equipped such that something big hits us, whatever it is, we are able to integrate that in awareness. Of course, it might take a while, it'll be of practice to echo out. And so we don't really have to you know, walk around going like this, or walk around going like... I can put my hands down. Ultimately, there's a world out there trying to get me, so we have to think about it, we have to feel it, we have to protect ourselves, and you know, always be on guard, and make sure we work hard. And you know, and so on and so forth, all the very different variations of that. 

